preparing tea
  Tea ia one of the God gift specially for winter season
    It's really simple to prepare tea.
     First take a tea pane and put a half cup of water in it.
     light the gas stove and put pane onto it.
     wait for 2 min and then add some tea leaves into the pane.
     when water start boiling add half cup milk in it.
     wait for 3 more min and then add 1 spoon sugar into it.
     and after half min add some ginger and cardoman and after another half min ur tea is ready.
